data.description: Why wait on new construction when this gorgeous, move-in ready home is available now?! Sit on the covered front porch & admire the wonderful neighborhood of McCormick Meadows at this 2,479 sf home. The kitchen is sure to make your dream a reality with granite countertops, SS appliances (with gas stove), & tons of storage space! Time to be spoiled with the oversized Primary Suite. Retreat to your own spa-like Primary bathroom, with soaking tub, shower, & walk-in closet. Two additional well appointed bedrooms upstairs, plus a full bath. Don't forget to bring an extra couch & make the perfect hangout room in the spacious loft! Home also includes A/C! Walk to the parks, or enjoy the easy drive to Bremerton or Gig Harbor!
